WEBVTT

00:08:00.222 --> 00:08:01.569
Ambayo ni nzuri,

00:08:01.593 --> 00:08:04.473
sababu inamaanisha kila siku
ninagundua kitu kipya.

00:08:04.497 --> 00:08:05.988
na kwenye hiyo harakati,

00:08:06.012 --> 00:08:09.906
kuangalia pembeni na kuona
mamia na maelfu ya vitu

00:08:09.930 --> 00:08:11.231
nisingeweza kujua.

00:08:12.964 --> 00:08:15.430
Maarifa ni zawadi kubwa sana.

00:08:16.452 --> 00:08:21.007
Lakini maarifa ya uwongo
yanaweza kua hatari kuliko ujinga.

00:08:21.895 --> 00:08:24.528
Kuwaza kwamba unamjua mpenzi wako

00:08:25.115 --> 00:08:26.272
au adui yako

00:08:26.621 --> 00:08:28.076
inaweza kua ya hila zaidi

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:30.548
kuliko kukubali kwamba hautowajua.